# Cambiar según sea necesario para apuntar a tu instancia local o de desarrollo.
@host = https://localhost:5001
@taskId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

# Generar con:
# dotnet user-jwts create --project ./src/TaskManagement.API/TaskManagement.API.csproj --audience https://localhost:5001 --audience http://localhost:5000 --claim nameid=11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111 --claim name=dev-user --output token
@bearerToken = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..ievH6W81g0ub7oPXgNDyXpSIOonVEpeYAqOS3e1lt_w

### Create Task
# This endpoint reads CreatedBy from User.GetUserId(), so use a token that contains NameIdentifier (sub/nameid).
POST {{host}}/api/tasks
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Finish Clean Architecture demo",
  "description": "Wire up in-memory SQLite and verify endpoint tests",
  "priority": "High",
  "dueDate": "2026-05-20T18:00:00Z"
}

### Get Task By Id
GET {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}
Accept: application/json

### Complete Task
POST {{host}}/api/tasks/{{taskId}}/complete
Accept: application/json
